description:
Welcome back, Trent.
Back by popular demand, Trent has really been working out and you can tell how he's put on some impressive muscle. Along with his increased muscle mass, somehow his sex drive increased as well... and it was already sky-high to begin with. Lucky for us, we were able to provide an outlet for release. He's just as handsome as ever though, and we're thrilled to have him back.
Watch Trent as he relaxes in the shower. Afterwards, he gets down to business in the living room as he works himself up to a creamy finale.
title: Trent
